  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Beacon node only verifies justified_block is stored in the DB by doing a lookup using justified_block_hash. \r\nhttps://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/master/beacon-chain/types/block.go#L266-L271\r\n\r\nInstead of verifying justified block has to be in the current chain, one more additional check needs to be implemented: Beacon node needs to verify the justified block's slot number is the same as justified_slot\r\n\r\nFrom spec:\r\n`Verify that justified_block_hash is the hash of the block in the current chain at the slot -- justified_slot`",
